{"tid":2305981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府斥4.5億推「法治教育」主攻中小學生 鄭若驊：抨擊警察不正確 憂慮他人誤解香港法治","createTime":"2020-11-30T06:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T07:18:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"24ee4175e9ec25b8e61243847607837f8a7995b9","tid":2305981,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"在今年2月的《財政預算案》中，政府宣佈預留4.5億元，讓律政司推行「願景2030&mdash;聚焦法治」計劃，以加深香港社會對法治概念的認識及實踐。律政司司長鄭若驊接受《星島日報》專訪時解釋，自去年起開始盛行「許多不正確的法治觀念、違法達義」等說法，令法治受衝擊，國際上有不少抨擊本港法治制度和警察表現的聲音，因此「要做多些法治工作」。她又透露，目前計劃已落實4項活動，暫時以教育界為主，在中小學的師生間推廣法治。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊在專訪上提到，計劃目標是推廣正確的法治教育並配合「一帶一路」，建立良好法治環境。又指去年起開始盛行「許多不正確的法治觀念、違法達義」等說法，令法治受衝擊，引來國際上不少聲音，抨擊本港法治制度和警察表現，因此「要做多些法治工作」，在本地推廣《基本法》和憲法教育，改善法治發展。她又透露，目前計劃已落實4項活動，暫時以教育界為主，在中小學的師生間推廣法治。她形容計劃「比較ambitious（有野心），但好需要」，因為憂慮他人會誤解香港法治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201130/YUTO6VMBVJF4PFQKB4BYOWOI4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201130%2FYUTO6VMBVJF4PFQKB4BYOWOI4U%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGifDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=9e8c31fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201130%2FYUTO6VMBVJF4PFQKB4BYOWOI4U%2F&h=9d834e15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201130/YUTO6VMBVJF4PFQKB4BYOWOI4U/</a>"},{"pid":"ad1efb82f509567a922a28c954884a87f596fc48","tid":2305981,"uid":18477,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"你個<strong><span class=\"red\">法</span></strong>可以搓圓撳扁<br />\n仲有乜嘢講啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93471b89cc8ac14490bbeb6b3ff1e862f94786f","tid":2305981,"uid":321002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"老老實實叫政治正確教育啦.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2e346b2dd57b7bbde66884fbd66165e5756631","tid":2305981,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:12:07.000Z","msg":"幾多錢律政司先肯出賣佢？"},{"pid":"dec21a05cd98defd36c90c7c707a623957807c00","tid":2305981,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:12:26.000Z","msg":"黑狗打人就正確?"},{"pid":"6d810d7988dbb34083b767d67e317ed82ca0d0fe","tid":2305981,"uid":221343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"聖人都有錯,但黑警就唔會錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9be43e2c33610cb8d4c962078251b28396aebc","tid":2305981,"uid":352936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:13:58.000Z","msg":"全世界都錯 政府無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f04b2fc102fddfb739529d049e0c6fa25adc12a","tid":2305981,"uid":51271,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.bannedbook.org/bnews/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/hkjb02.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannedbook.org%2Fbnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2Fhkjb02.gif&h=26fbe842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正確?"},{"pid":"5a10d1989355bdf63463f06488e911316630fd75","tid":2305981,"uid":66049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:16:09.000Z","msg":"死肥閪點解仲未死"},{"pid":"48d17d99427eefe9d11b059bc588345797ea60f0","tid":2305981,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6e99d5d6f0e6b1532a4ecce4b518f348eeddd2","tid":2305981,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike"